         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 24, Mecheir 15. (Give) from the account of Julius Theon the functioning archidikastes to Malius Antoninus the linen-seller, for the price of linen goods from Apollon, 6 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Give the 6 drachmas."</ab>
